<div class="file-content md">
<h1 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="1:1-1:10">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#keycloak" class="anchor" id="user-content-keycloak"></a>Keycloak</h1>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="3:1-3:104">Keycloak is an Open Source Identity and Access Management solution for modern Applications and Services.</p>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="5:1-5:107">This repository contains the source code for the Keycloak Server, Java adapters and the JavaScript adapter.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="8:1-8:25">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#help-and-documentation" class="anchor" id="user-content-help-and-documentation"></a>Help and Documentation</h2>
<ul dir="auto" data-sourcepos="10:1-13:0">
<li data-sourcepos="10:1-10:62"><a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.keycloak.org/documentation.html" target="_blank">Documentation</a></li>
<li data-sourcepos="11:1-13:0">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://groups.google.com/d/forum/keycloak-user" target="_blank">User Mailing List</a> - Mailing list for help and general questions about Keycloak</li>
</ul>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="14:1-14:37">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#reporting-security-vulnerabilities" class="anchor" id="user-content-reporting-security-vulnerabilities"></a>Reporting Security Vulnerabilities</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="16:1-16:158">If you've found a security vulnerability, please look at the <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/security/policy" target="_blank">instructions on how to properly report it</a></p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="19:1-19:21">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#reporting-an-issue" class="anchor" id="user-content-reporting-an-issue"></a>Reporting an issue</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="21:1-22:95">If you believe you have discovered a defect in Keycloak, please open <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/issues" target="_blank">an issue</a>.
Please remember to provide a good summary, description as well as steps to reproduce the issue.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="25:1-25:18">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#getting-started" class="anchor" id="user-content-getting-started"></a>Getting started</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="27:1-27:118">To run Keycloak, download the distribution from our <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.keycloak.org/downloads.html" target="_blank">website</a>. Unzip and run:</p>
<div class="gl-relative markdown-code-block js-markdown-code">
<pre data-canonical-lang="" class="code highlight js-syntax-highlight language-plaintext white" lang="plaintext" data-sourcepos="29:5-30:0" id="code-2"><code><span lang="plaintext" class="line" id="LC1">bin/kc.[sh|bat] start-dev</span></code></pre>
<copy-code><button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-md gl-button btn-icon has-tooltip" data-title="Copy to clipboard" data-clipboard-target="pre#code-2"><svg><use xlink:href="/assets/icons-ce4e8ebe16c824ec266af5c86cfa08b0d35e88b4fa857e862dd87bbc726986bc.svg#copy-to-clipboard"></use></svg></button></copy-code>
</div>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="31:1-31:55">Alternatively, you can use the Docker image by running:</p>
<div class="gl-relative markdown-code-block js-markdown-code">
<pre data-canonical-lang="" class="code highlight js-syntax-highlight language-plaintext white" lang="plaintext" data-sourcepos="33:5-34:4" id="code-3"><code><span lang="plaintext" class="line" id="LC1">docker run quay.io/keycloak/keycloak start-dev</span></code></pre>
<copy-code><button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-md gl-button btn-icon has-tooltip" data-title="Copy to clipboard" data-clipboard-target="pre#code-3"><svg><use xlink:href="/assets/icons-ce4e8ebe16c824ec266af5c86cfa08b0d35e88b4fa857e862dd87bbc726986bc.svg#copy-to-clipboard"></use></svg></button></copy-code>
</div>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="35:1-35:100">For more details refer to the <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.keycloak.org/documentation.html" target="_blank">Keycloak Documentation</a>.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="38:1-38:23">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#building-from-source" class="anchor" id="user-content-building-from-source"></a>Building from Source</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="40:1-40:101">To build from source, refer to the <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/docs/building.md">building and working with the code base</a> guide.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="43:1-43:11">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#testing" class="anchor" id="user-content-testing"></a>Testing</h3>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="45:1-45:64">To run tests, refer to the <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/docs/tests.md">running tests</a> guide.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="48:1-48:17">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#writing-tests" class="anchor" id="user-content-writing-tests"></a>Writing Tests</h3>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="50:1-50:78">To write tests, refer to the <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/docs/tests-development.md">writing tests</a> guide.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="53:1-53:15">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#contributing" class="anchor" id="user-content-contributing"></a>Contributing</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="55:1-55:92">Before contributing to Keycloak, please read our <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">contributing guidelines</a>.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="58:1-58:26">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#other-keycloak-projects" class="anchor" id="user-content-other-keycloak-projects"></a>Other Keycloak Projects</h2>
<ul dir="auto" data-sourcepos="60:1-66:0">
<li data-sourcepos="60:1-60:86">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak" target="_blank">Keycloak</a> - Keycloak Server and Java adapters</li>

<h1 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="1:1-1:10">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#keycloak" class="anchor" id="user-content-keycloak"></a>Keycloak</h1>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="3:1-3:104">Keycloak is an Open Source Identity and Access Management solution for modern Applications and Services.</p>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="5:1-5:107">This repository contains the source code for the Keycloak Server, Java adapters and the JavaScript adapter.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="8:1-8:25">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#help-and-documentation" class="anchor" id="user-content-help-and-documentation"></a>Help and Documentation</h2>
<ul dir="auto" data-sourcepos="10:1-13:0">
<li data-sourcepos="10:1-10:62"><a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.keycloak.org/documentation.html" target="_blank">Documentation</a></li>
<li data-sourcepos="11:1-13:0">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://groups.google.com/d/forum/keycloak-user" target="_blank">User Mailing List</a> - Mailing list for help and general questions about Keycloak</li>
</ul>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="14:1-14:37">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#reporting-security-vulnerabilities" class="anchor" id="user-content-reporting-security-vulnerabilities"></a>Reporting Security Vulnerabilities</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="16:1-16:158">If you've found a security vulnerability, please look at the <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/security/policy" target="_blank">instructions on how to properly report it</a></p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="19:1-19:21">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#reporting-an-issue" class="anchor" id="user-content-reporting-an-issue"></a>Reporting an issue</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="21:1-22:95">If you believe you have discovered a defect in Keycloak, please open <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/issues" target="_blank">an issue</a>.
Please remember to provide a good summary, description as well as steps to reproduce the issue.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="25:1-25:18">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#getting-started" class="anchor" id="user-content-getting-started"></a>Getting started</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="27:1-27:118">To run Keycloak, download the distribution from our <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.keycloak.org/downloads.html" target="_blank">website</a>. Unzip and run:</p>
<div class="gl-relative markdown-code-block js-markdown-code">
<pre data-canonical-lang="" class="code highlight js-syntax-highlight language-plaintext white" lang="plaintext" data-sourcepos="29:5-30:0" id="code-2"><code><span lang="plaintext" class="line" id="LC1">bin/kc.[sh|bat] start-dev</span></code></pre>
<copy-code><button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-md gl-button btn-icon has-tooltip" data-title="Copy to clipboard" data-clipboard-target="pre#code-2"><svg><use xlink:href="/assets/icons-ce4e8ebe16c824ec266af5c86cfa08b0d35e88b4fa857e862dd87bbc726986bc.svg#copy-to-clipboard"></use></svg></button></copy-code>
</div>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="31:1-31:55">Alternatively, you can use the Docker image by running:</p>
<div class="gl-relative markdown-code-block js-markdown-code">
<pre data-canonical-lang="" class="code highlight js-syntax-highlight language-plaintext white" lang="plaintext" data-sourcepos="33:5-34:4" id="code-3"><code><span lang="plaintext" class="line" id="LC1">docker run quay.io/keycloak/keycloak start-dev</span></code></pre>
<copy-code><button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-md gl-button btn-icon has-tooltip" data-title="Copy to clipboard" data-clipboard-target="pre#code-3"><svg><use xlink:href="/assets/icons-ce4e8ebe16c824ec266af5c86cfa08b0d35e88b4fa857e862dd87bbc726986bc.svg#copy-to-clipboard"></use></svg></button></copy-code>
</div>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="35:1-35:100">For more details refer to the <a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.keycloak.org/documentation.html" target="_blank">Keycloak Documentation</a>.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="38:1-38:23">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#building-from-source" class="anchor" id="user-content-building-from-source"></a>Building from Source</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="40:1-40:101">To build from source, refer to the <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/docs/building.md">building and working with the code base</a> guide.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="43:1-43:11">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#testing" class="anchor" id="user-content-testing"></a>Testing</h3>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="45:1-45:64">To run tests, refer to the <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/docs/tests.md">running tests</a> guide.</p>
<h3 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="48:1-48:17">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#writing-tests" class="anchor" id="user-content-writing-tests"></a>Writing Tests</h3>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="50:1-50:78">To write tests, refer to the <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/docs/tests-development.md">writing tests</a> guide.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="53:1-53:15">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#contributing" class="anchor" id="user-content-contributing"></a>Contributing</h2>
<p dir="auto" data-sourcepos="55:1-55:92">Before contributing to Keycloak, please read our <a class="gfm" href="/keycloak/keycloak/-/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">contributing guidelines</a>.</p>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="58:1-58:26">
<a aria-hidden="true" href="#other-keycloak-projects" class="anchor" id="user-content-other-keycloak-projects"></a>Other Keycloak Projects</h2>
<ul dir="auto" data-sourcepos="60:1-66:0">
<li data-sourcepos="60:1-60:86">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak" target="_blank">Keycloak</a> - Keycloak Server and Java adapters</li>
<li data-sourcepos="61:1-61:107">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak-documentation" target="_blank">Keycloak Documentation</a> - Documentation for Keycloak</li>
<li data-sourcepos="62:1-62:122">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak-quickstarts" target="_blank">Keycloak QuickStarts</a> - QuickStarts for getting started with Keycloak</li>
<li data-sourcepos="63:1-63:112">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak-nodejs-connect" target="_blank">Keycloak Node.js Connect</a> - Node.js adapter for Keycloak</li>
<li data-sourcepos="64:1-66:0">
<a rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" href="https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak-nodejs-admin-client" target="_blank">Keycloak Node.js Admin Client</a> - Node.js library for Keycloak Admin REST API</li>
</ul>
<h2 dir="auto" data-sourcepos="67:1-67:10">

</ul>

if ('loading' in HTMLImageElement.prototype) {
  document.querySelectorAll('img.lazy').forEach(img => {
    img.loading = 'lazy';
    let imgUrl = img.dataset.src;
    // Only adding width + height for avatars for now
    if (imgUrl.indexOf('/avatar/') > -1 && imgUrl.indexOf('?') === -1) {
      const targetWidth = img.getAttribute('width') || img.width;
      imgUrl += `?width=${targetWidth}`;
    }
    img.src = imgUrl;
    img.removeAttribute('data-src');
    img.classList.remove('lazy');
    img.classList.add('js-lazy-loaded');
    img.dataset.qa_selector = 'js_lazy_loaded_content';
  });
}

</script>
